item.title:
Laura Terruso’s ‘ABOUT MY FATHER’ starring Sebastian Maniscalco & Robert De Niro is now playing in theaters.
It follows Sebastian, who informs his traditional Italian father Salvo about his plan to propose to his American girlfriend. Salvo insists on joining them for a weekend.
